{"tid":2178911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"矢板明夫：中共下定決心同美國打長期戰 美中兩邊鬥拉表態国安法時投棄權既國家","createTime":"2020-08-28T17:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T17:32:01.000Z","uid":58841,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95736d91c62e29cf5867be68de9c6e7e44b329a1","tid":2178911,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T17:14:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w8VSWlT99J0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw8VSWlT99J0&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyI5RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=88f62945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w8VSWlT99J0</a><br />\n<br />\n国安法個陣<br />\n支那：53個窮閪國家<br />\n美國：27個發達國家<br />\n<br />\n但事實上例如意大利 捷克 南韓個陣都投左棄權<br />\n所以個陣王毅即刻去南韓搵文在寅傾<br />\n而家輪到去搵意大利 唔撚怪得之隔離POST講聰仔追住黎屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想暗訪就搞撚爛哂佢個行程<br />\n矢板明夫最尾有講下一任首相肯定無安倍咁親美 所以王毅絕對第一時間衝去日本暗訪<br />\n連登仔係時候發揮私怨撚狙擊精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14634248144029a833c9a6ca619545d892731169","tid":2178911,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T17:22:25.000Z","msg":"矢板：至於日本下一任首相，五觀未必有安倍咁端正，但三觀見得人既還大有人在"},{"pid":"01c6b907f965531bdbe688c5c038e7390507e14c","tid":2178911,"uid":253263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"下任日本首相更新美，成第六眼後中國永出不了第一島鏈。（路邊社）"}]}